{"tid":2088998,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"約翰遜：若中國續沿此路　將予BNO持有人成為公民途徑","createTime":"2020-07-01T12:47:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T12:55:28.000Z","uid":7542,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f393533095077793dcd1364443325dec305da8fa","tid":2088998,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T12:47:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中國政府拘捕約翰遜了嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n英國首相約翰遜批評北京訂立「港區國安法」，認為是明顯及嚴重違反《中英聯合聲明》，違反香港的高度自治，威脅聯合聲明所保障的自由與權利，與基本法有直接衝突，表明如果中方繼續沿著這條道路前進，英方將會向英國國民海外護照BNO持有人，提供成為英國公民的新途徑。外相藍韜文透露，BNO持有人將可以留在英國工作或學習五年，之後可以申請定居身份，定居滿12個月後，就可以申請成為英國公民，有關措施將不設配額。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535256-20200701.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535256-20200701.htm&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffbgCffgmrlYx1zcVg66SIO7I%3D&h=013039f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535256-20200701.htm&h=55553fb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535256-20200701.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tattalk3/status/1278260306112724992?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftattalk3%2Fstatus%2F1278260306112724992%3Fs%3D21&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffbgCffgmrlYx1zcVg66SIO7I%3D&h=bb4da3df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftattalk3%2Fstatus%2F1278260306112724992%3Fs%3D21&h=149ea92c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tattalk3/status/1278260306112724992?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"6ec7a7d8f0f0017fc1adcc9c43de623edf4bc535","tid":2088998,"uid":51583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T12:48:37.000Z","msg":"若中國續沿此路?<br />\n仲未CONFIRM此路有問題?"},{"pid":"c7d7139ca3cf563f3440a36f93dfa876782